itunes:subtitle: Rachael Ray is the New York Times bestselling author of more than 20 cookbooks, the host of multiple cooking shows, and the star of syndicated talk show "Rachael Ray." The Apple Store, SoHo hosted Rachael to talk about her latest book, My Year in Meals.
